headline: ONEOK Adds Experienced Directors As Valuation And Momentum Draw Attention
summary: ONEOK (NYSE:OKE) has appointed Mark A. McCollum and Precious Williams Owodunni as independent directors to its board. Both new directors bring extensive energy sector, corporate strategy, and boardroom experience. Their election represents a governance development for ONEOK and its stakeholders.
